description.en: Potter Inu is a ERC20 Coin for the fans of Harry Potter. Potter just sat on his Nimbus 2021 Decentralized Racing Broom and he is aiming for the moon. He does not want to go alone this is a project where the investor is an active contributor to the success. All investors in the pack will be working together to reach the moon and beyond. Every investor is able to vote and create ideas that can improve the ecosystem. Hop on now on the Hogwarts Express if you don’t want to miss this.
